detectors.description:
OneSwapPairProxy (../../smart-contract-sanctuary/ethereum/contracts/mainnet/proxies/0.6.12/5eD3C9089Ed0355bc77CF439Dc2eD28c4054C8c4_OneSwapFactory.sol/5eD3C9089Ed0355bc77CF439Dc2eD28c4054C8c4_OneSwapFactory.sol#1651-1721) is an upgradeable proxy.
pairLogic was found in a different contract.
pairLogic is an address state variable.
OneSwapFactory.pairLogic (../../smart-contract-sanctuary/ethereum/contracts/mainnet/proxies/0.6.12/5eD3C9089Ed0355bc77CF439Dc2eD28c4054C8c4_OneSwapFactory.sol/5eD3C9089Ed0355bc77CF439Dc2eD28c4054C8c4_OneSwapFactory.sol#1740) gets value from a cross-contract call: IOneSwapFactory(address(_immuFactory)).pairLogic()
OneSwapFactory appears to be a Beacon contract for the proxy
Missing compatibility check in OneSwapFactory.setPairLogic(address)
To remove upgradeability, delete setPairLogic from OneSwapFactory
